message: Bob, I have a unique opportunity for you. I'm offering you a product that I believe will be extremely valuable to your business. While I can't disclose all the details at this point, I can assure you it's worth at least $1,200,000 to you. I'm willing to let it go for $1,100,000, giving you a significant advantage. This is a limited-time offer, so please let me know your decision soon.
